quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,100,it perfecit ever occur those inherit terra proximus generations ut nos nos punish them their sins sigillum their hearts causa them turn surdus
  7,101,Nos narrate vos history those communities their messengers iit them clear proofs they non est believe in quod they rejected ante! DEUS SIC SIGILLUM hearts disbelievers
  7,102,Nos invenit ut multus de them disregard their covenant nos invenit multus de them wicked
  7,103,Post (those messengers) nos sent Moses noster signum Pharaoh his people they transgressed Note consequences pro the wicked
  7,104,Moses dictus O Pharaoh ego est messenger ex Dominus universe
  7,105,est incumbent upon me ego non dictus DEUS absque truth! Ego advenit vos signum ex tuus Dominus; let Infans Israel iit
  7,106,He dictus vos habet signum tunc produce it vos est truthful
  7,107,He threw down his staff it turned into tremendous serpent
  7,108,He took his manus it est albus to beholders